* **Layouts:** 1–3 Spalten, Karussell
* **Einstellungen:** Name, Bild, Text, Sterne, Alter, Filter
* **Presets:** Card Wide, Quote Overlay, Grid Cards, Carousel, Mini-Review

### 8. Pricing-Block
